<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
    <title>Payment Failed</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        body {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .payment-failed-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .retry-btn {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .retry-btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="payment-failed-container">
        <h2 class="text-danger">Payment Failed</h2>
        <p>We regret to inform you that your recent payment attempt has failed for the following transaction:</p>

        <dl class="row">
            <dt class="col-sm-4">Transaction ID:</dt>
            <dd class="col-sm-8">[Transaction ID]</dd>

            <dt class="col-sm-4">Amount:</dt>
            <dd class="col-sm-8">[Amount]</dd>

            <dt class="col-sm-4">Date and Time:</dt>
            <dd class="col-sm-8">[Date and Time]</dd>
        </dl>

        <p><strong>Reason for Failure:</strong> [Provide a brief description of the reason for the payment failure.]</p>

        <div class="text-center">
            <p>To ensure uninterrupted access to our services, please retry the payment:</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary retry-btn">Retry Payment</a>
        </div>

        <p>If you encounter any difficulties or have questions, please contact our customer support at <a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>.</p>

        <p>We appreciate your prompt attention to this matter and apologize for any inconvenience caused. Thank you for your continued support.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS and dependencies -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

</body>

</html>
